    "title": "Hiring Category Manager at Urban Ladder",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Urban Ladder. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Category Manager to strengthen our Mumbai-based team.\n\nAbout Urban Ladder:\nUrban Ladder is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Magento\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Urban Ladder!",
